title: 140: Week 13 preview, where to find a QB, CFB and more
itunes:title: 140: Week 13 preview, where to find a QB, CFB and more
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks chat about the best route teams should take when looking for a new QB. Are they worth a high draft pick in 2017 or would Jimmy Garoppolo and AJ McCarron be more valuable? DJ and Bucky also break down the scouting reports on Khalil Mack and current college football stars. The duo also make their NFL and college game picks.
